Package com.herocraftonline.dthielke.lists

Class Summary
Lists Bukkit plugin which allows users to create persistent lists of players that can be accessed and modified by other plugins.
PrivilegedList Stores a list of players that can be created by users and passed between plugins.
 

Enum Summary
Lists.Permission Internal usage only.
PrivilegedList.PrivilegeLevel Enumeration of the four available privilege levels for members of a list.
